 
<p>
  *More than 180 British Council contractors left trapped in
  Afghanistan have been given immediate permission by the UK
  government to <a href="https://www.theguardian.com/world/2022/jul/04/fears-for-british-council-staff-trapped-in-afghanistan-despite-breakthrough">apply online to come to Britain, but no hint of how to
  get out of the country safely</a>.*
<p>
  It appears that UK bureaucrats followed their standard practice, with
  all would-be immigrants, of looking for excuses to refuse to let them
  in.  It must have become a habit for them.

 